      {
        "number": 70,
        "name": "سُورَةُ المَعَارِجِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Ma'aarij",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Ascending Stairways",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5376,
            "text": "Someone has (needlessly) demanded to experience the torment (of God),",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5377,
            "text": "which will inevitably seize the disbelievers.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5378,
            "text": "No one can defend him against God, the Lord of the exalted positions.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5379,
            "text": "On that Day (of Judgment), long as fifty thousand years, the angels and the Spirit will ascend to Him.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5380,
            "text": "(Muhammad), exercise patience with no complaints.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5381,
            "text": "They think that it (the Day of Judgment) is far away.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5382,
            "text": "but We see it to be very near.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5383,
            "text": "On the day when the heavens become like molten metal.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5384,
            "text": "and the mountains become like wool,",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5385,
            "text": "even intimate friends will not inquire about their friends,",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5386,
            "text": "though they may see each other. A sinner will wish that he could save himself from the torment of that day by sacrificing his children,",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5387,
            "text": "his wife, his brother,",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5388,
            "text": "his kinsmen who gave him refuge (from hardship)",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5389,
            "text": "and all those on earth.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5390,
            "text": "By no means! For the raging flames of the fire",
