      {
        "number": 71,
        "name": "سُورَةُ نُوحٍ",
        "englishName": "Nooh",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Noah",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5420,
            "text": "We sent Noah to his people telling him, 'Warn your people before a painful torment approaches them'.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5421,
            "text": "Noah said, 'My people, I am warning you plainly.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5422,
            "text": "Worship God, have fear of Him and obey me.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5423,
            "text": "He will forgive your sins and give you a respite for an appointed time. When the time which God has appointed arrives, none will be able to postpone it. Would that you knew this!'",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5424,
            "text": "Noah said, 'My Lord, I have been preaching to my people, night and day,",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5425,
            "text": "but it has had no effect on them except to make them run away.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5426,
            "text": "Evert time I invite them to Your (guidance) so that You can forgive them, they put their fingers into their ears, cover their heads with their clothes, persist in their disbelief and display extreme arrogance.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5427,
            "text": "'I preached to them aloud, in public.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5428,
            "text": "Then I conveyed the message to them, again, both in public and in private,",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5429,
            "text": "and told them, 'Ask forgiveness from your Lord; He is All-forgiving'.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5430,
            "text": "He will send you abundant",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5431,
            "text": "rain from the sky,",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5432,
            "text": "strengthen you by (providing) you wealth and children, and make gardens and streams for you. What is the matter with you that you are not afraid of the greatness of God",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5433,
            "text": "who has created you in several stages?",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5434,
            "text": "'Have you not seen that God has created the seven heavens one above the other",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5435,
            "text": "and placed therein the moon as a light",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5436,
            "text": "and the sun as a torch.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5437,
            "text": "God made you grow from the earth. He will make you return to it and then take you out of it again.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5438,
            "text": "God has spread out the earth",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5439,
            "text": "for you, so that you may walk along its wide roads'.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5440,
            "text": "Noah said, 'Lord, they have disobeyed me and followed those whose wealth and children will only bring about destruction for them.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 505,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5441,
            "text": "They have arrogantly plotted evil plans against me,",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 505,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5442,
            "text": "and have said to each other, 'Do not give-up your idols. Do not renounce Wadd, Suwa`, Yaghuth, Ya`uq and Nasr (names of certain idols).",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 505,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5443,
            "text": "They have misled many and the unjust will achieve nothing but more error'.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 505,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5444,
            "text": "Because of their sins, they were drowned and made to enter hell. They could find no one to help them besides God.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 505,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5445,
            "text": "Noah said, 'Lord, do not leave a single disbeliever on earth;",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 505,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5446,
            "text": "if You do, they will mislead Your servants and will only give birth to ungrateful sinners.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 505,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5447,
            "text": "Lord, forgive me, my parents, the believers who have entered my home and all believing men and women. Give nothing to the unjust but destruction.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 505,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 72,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الجِنِّ",
        "englishName": "Al-Jinn",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Jinn",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5448,
            "text": "(Muhammad), say, 'It has been revealed to me that a party of jinn has listened (to the recitation) of the Quran and has told (their people), 'We heard an amazing reading",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5449,
            "text": "which guides people to the right path and we believe in it. We shall never consider anyone equal to our Lord;",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5450,
            "text": "our Lord is too exalted to have either a wife or son.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5451,
            "text": "The dimwit one (the devil) among us has been telling confused lies about God.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5452,
            "text": "We thought that no man or jinn could ever tell lies about God.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5453,
            "text": "'Certain human beings sought refuge with certain jinn and this increased the rebelliousness of those jinn.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5454,
            "text": "Those people thought, like you, that God would never send down a Messenger.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5455,
            "text": "'We went near the heavens but found it to be full of strong guards and shooting flames.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5456,
            "text": "We used to sit near by and try to listen to the heavens, but shooting flames now await those who try to do that.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5457,
            "text": "We do not know whether by this arrangement God intends benefit and guidance for the people of the earth or only evil.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5458,
            "text": "As for us, some of us are righteous and others are not. We have all followed different ways.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5459,
            "text": "We knew that we could never challenge God whether we stayed on earth or fled elsewhere.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5460,
            "text": "Now that we have listened to the guidance, we believe in it. Whoever believes in his Lord does not need to fear loss or oppression.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5461,
            "text": "Some of us are Muslims and some of us have deviated from the Truth. Whoever has embraced Islam has followed the right guidance.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5462,
            "text": "However, the deviators from the Truth will be the fuel for hell'.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5463,
            "text": "Had they (jinn and mankind) remained steadfast in their religion (Islam), We would certainly have given them abundant water to drink",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5464,
            "text": "as a trial for them. God will make those who disregard the guidance from their Lord suffer increasing torment.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5465,
            "text": "All the parts of the body to be placed on the ground during prostration belong to God.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5466,
            "text": "Do not prostrate before anyone other than Him. When the servant of God (Muhammad) preached (his message) the jinn would all crowd around him.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5467,
            "text": "(Muhammad), say, 'I worship only my Lord and do not consider anyone equal to Him'.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 507,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5468,
            "text": "Say, 'I do not possess any power to harm or benefit you'.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 507,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5469,
            "text": "Say, 'No one can protect me from God, nor can I find any place of refuge but with him.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 507,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5470,
            "text": "My only (means of protection) is to convey the message of God. Whoever disobeys God and His Messenger will go to hell, wherein he will live forever'.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 507,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5471,
            "text": "(On the Day of Judgment) when the disbelievers witness that with which they have been threatened, they will then know whose helpers are weaker and fewer in number.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 507,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5472,
            "text": "(Muhammad), say, 'I do not know whether that with which you have been threatened is close by or whether my Lord will prolong the time of its coming.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 507,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5473,
            "text": "He knows the unseen and He does not allow anyone to know His secrets except those of His Messengers whom He chooses.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 507,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5474,
            "text": "He causes angelic guards to march before and after him.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 507,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5475,
            "text": "(Messenger) so that He would know that the Messengers have conveyed the message of their Lord. He encompasses all that is with them and He keeps a precise account of all things'.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 507,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 73,
        "name": "سُورَةُ المُزَّمِّلِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Muzzammil",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Enshrouded One",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5476,
            "text": "You, who have wrapped yourself up with a mantle,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5477,
            "text": "worship (God) for a few hours at night.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5478,
            "text": "(Worship Him) for more or less than half of the night",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5479,
            "text": "and recite the Quran in a distinct tone;",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5480,
            "text": "We are about to reveal to you a mighty word.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5481,
            "text": "Prayer at night leaves the strongest impression on one's soul and the words spoken are more consistent.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5482,
            "text": "During the day, you are preoccupied with many activities.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5483,
            "text": "Glorify the Name of your Lord, the Lord of the eastern and western regions, with due sincerity.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5484,
            "text": "He is the only Lord, so choose Him as your guardian.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5485,
            "text": "Bear patiently whatever they say, do not yield to them and keep on preaching decently to them.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5486,
            "text": "Leave the prosperous disbelievers to Me and give them respite for a little while;",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5487,
            "text": "We have prepared for them fetters, flaming fire,",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5488,
            "text": "food which chokes (them), and a painful torment.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5489,
            "text": "On that day, the earth and the mountains will be violently shaken, and the mountains will be turned into heaps of moving sand.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5490,
            "text": "We have sent you a Messenger, who will witness your deeds, just as We sent a Messenger to the Pharaoh.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5491,
            "text": "However, the Pharaoh disobeyed the Messenger and We seized him with a severe retribution.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5492,
            "text": "If you, disbelieve, how will you be able to protect yourselves from the hardships of the day which would even turn children grey-headed?",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5493,
            "text": "On that day, the heavens will be rent asunder. This is the decree of God which has already been ordained.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5494,
            "text": "This is a reminder. Let anyone who wants, seek guidance from his Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5495,
            "text": "Your Lord knows that you and a group of those who are with you get up for prayer sometimes for less than two-thirds of the night, sometimes half and sometimes one-third of it. God determines the duration of the night and day. He knew that it would be hard for you to keep an exact account of the timing of the night prayers, so He turned to you with forgiveness. Thus, recite from the Quran as much as possible. He knew that some of you would be sick, others would travel in the land to seek God's favors, and still others would fight for the cause of God. Thus, recite from the Quran as much as possible, be steadfast in prayer, pay the zakat, and give virtuous loans to God. Whatever good deeds you save for the next life, you will certainly find them with God. This is the best investment, and for this you will find the greatest reward. Ask forgiveness from God. God is All-forgiving and All-merciful.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 509,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 74,
        "name": "سُورَةُ المُدَّثِّرِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Muddaththir",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Cloaked One",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5496,
            "text": "Cloaked one,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
