            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5501,
            "text": "and do not think that by doing such deeds, you have done a great favor to God.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5502,
            "text": "Exercise patience to please your Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5503,
            "text": "When the trumpet is sounded,.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5504,
            "text": "it will be a hard day",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5505,
            "text": "and for the disbelievers, in particular, it will not be at all easy.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5506,
            "text": "Leave to Me the one, whom I have created all by Myself,",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5507,
            "text": "and whom I have granted abundant wealth",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5508,
            "text": "and children living in his presence,",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5509,
            "text": "whose life I have made run smoothly",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5510,
            "text": "and who still desires more.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5511,
            "text": "Never will he receive more. He has been hostile to Our revelations.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5512,
            "text": "We shall make him suffer the torment of hell without relief.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 575,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5513,
            "text": "He planned and plotted.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5514,
            "text": "May he be condemned!",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5515,
            "text": "What an evil plan he has made!",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5516,
            "text": "May he be condemned again for his schemes! He looked around,",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5517,
            "text": "frowned and scowled,",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5518,
            "text": "then turned back, and swelling-up with pride,",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5519,
            "text": "said, 'This (the Quran) is nothing but magic, inherited from ancient magicians.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5520,
            "text": "These are only words from a mere mortal'.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5521,
            "text": "I shall make him suffer the torment of hell.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5522,
            "text": "Would that you really knew what hell is!",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5523,
            "text": "It leaves and spares no one and nothing.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5524,
            "text": "It scorches people's skin",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5525,
            "text": "and it has nineteen angelic keepers.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5526,
            "text": "We have made only angels as the keepers of the fire (for they are the strongest in carrying out Our commands). Our informing (people) of the numbers of these angels is a trial for the disbelievers. It gives more certainty to the people of the Book and strengthens the faith of the believers. The people of the Book and the believers have no doubt about it. We have fixed the number to make the disbelievers and those whose hearts are sick say, 'What does God mean by such a parable?' Thus, God guides and causes to go astray whomever He wants. No one knows about the army of your Lord except He Himself. This parable is a reminder for mankind.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 510,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5527,
            "text": "By the moon,",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5528,
            "text": "by the retreating night,",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5529,
            "text": "by the brightening dawn,",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5530,
            "text": "hell is certainly the greatest calamity.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5531,
            "text": "It is a warning for mankind",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5532,
            "text": "whether one steps forward to embrace the faith or one turns away from it.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5533,
            "text": "Every soul will be in captivity for its deeds",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5534,
            "text": "except the people of the right hand",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5535,
            "text": "who will be in Paradise",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5536,
            "text": "and will ask of the criminals,",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5537,
            "text": "'what led you into hell?'",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5538,
            "text": "They will reply, 'We did not pray,",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5539,
            "text": "nor did we feed the destitute.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5540,
            "text": "We indulged and persisted in useless disputes,",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5541,
            "text": "and rejected the Day of Judgment",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5542,
            "text": "until death approached us'.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 576,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5543,
            "text": "The intercession of the intercessors will be of no benefit to them.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5544,
            "text": "If such will be the Day of Judgment, what is the matter with them? Why do they run away from guidance,",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5545,
            "text": "like frightened donkeys",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5546,
            "text": "running away from a lion?",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5547,
            "text": "Is it that everyone of them wants to receive a heavenly book addressed to him personally?",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5548,
            "text": "This will certainly never be the case! In fact, they are not afraid of the Day of Judgment.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5549,
            "text": "There is no doubt that the Quran is a guide.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5550,
            "text": "Let anyone who seeks guidance do so.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5551,
            "text": "No one will seek guidance unless God wills it. He alone is worthy of being feared and He is the Source of Forgiveness.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 75,
        "name": "سُورَةُ القِيَامَةِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Qiyaama",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Resurrection",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5552,
            "text": "I swear by the Day of Resurrection",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5553,
            "text": "and by the self accusing soul (that you will certainly be resurrected).",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5554,
            "text": "Do men think that We shall never be able to assemble their bones?",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5555,
            "text": "We certainly have the power to restore them even the very tips of their finger.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5556,
            "text": "In fact, people want to have eternal life in this world.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5557,
            "text": "He asks, 'When will be the Day of Judgment?'",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5558,
            "text": "When the eye is bewildered,",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5559,
            "text": "the moon eclipsed.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5560,
            "text": "and the sun and the moon are brought together,",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5561,
            "text": "people will say, 'Is there anywhere to run away?'",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5562,
            "text": "Certainly not! There will be no place of refuge.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5563,
            "text": "The only place of refuge will be with God.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5564,
            "text": "On that day, people will be informed of all that they had done and all that they were supposed to do.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5565,
            "text": "In fact, people are well-aware of their own soul",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5566,
            "text": "even though they make excuses.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5567,
            "text": "(Muhammad), do not move your tongue too quickly to recite the Quran.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5568,
            "text": "We shall be responsible for its collection and its recitation.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5569,
            "text": "When We recite it, follow its recitation (by Us).",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5570,
            "text": "We shall be responsible for its explanation.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5571,
            "text": "Human beings certainly do not want to pay much attention to the Quran. In fact, they love the worldly life",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5572,
            "text": "and neglect the life to come.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5573,
            "text": "On the Day of Judgment some faces will be bright,",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5574,
            "text": "and look forward to receiving mercy from their Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5575,
            "text": "Others will be despondent,",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5576,
            "text": "certain of facing a great calamity.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5577,
            "text": "Some people, certainly, do not believe in it, but when a person's soul reaches up to his throat",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5578,
            "text": "and the angels say, 'Who will take away his soul,",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5579,
            "text": "(the angels of mercy or the angels of wrath,)' then, he will realize that it is time to leave this world.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5580,
            "text": "When legs are twisted around each other,",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5581,
            "text": "that will be the time to be driven to one's Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5582,
            "text": "The human being does not want to believe the Truth, nor does he want to pray.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5583,
            "text": "He rejects the faith, turns away",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5584,
            "text": "and haughtily goes to his people.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5585,
            "text": "Woe to you!",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5586,
            "text": "Woe to you!",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5587,
            "text": "For you, the human being of such behavior, will certainly deserve it.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5588,
            "text": "Does the human being think that he will be left uncontrolled?",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5589,
            "text": "Was he not once just a drop of discharged sperm.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5590,
            "text": "Was he not turned into a clot of blood? God then formed him and gave him proper shape. From the human being, God made males and females in pairs.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5591,
            "text": "Does He then not have the power to bring the dead back to life?",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 76,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الإِنسَانِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Insaan",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Man",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5592,
            "text": "There was certainly a time when there was no mention of the human being.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5593,
            "text": "We created the human being from the union of sperm and egg to test him. We gave him hearing and vision.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5594,
            "text": "We showed him the right path whether he would be grateful or ungrateful.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5595,
            "text": "We have prepared chains, shackles, and flaming fire (for the disbelievers).",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5596,
            "text": "The virtuous ones will drink from a cup containing camphor",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5597,
            "text": "which flows from a spring from which the servants of God will drink.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5598,
            "text": "The servants of God fulfill their vows and are afraid of the day in which there will be widespread terror.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5599,
            "text": "They feed the destitute, orphans, and captives for the love of God, saying,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5600,
            "text": "'We only feed you for the sake of God and we do not want any reward or thanks from you.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5601,
            "text": "We are afraid of our Lord and the bitterly distressful day'.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5602,
            "text": "God will certainly rescue them from the terror of that day and will meet them with joy and pleasure.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5603,
            "text": "For their patience, He will reward them with Paradise and silk.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5604,
            "text": "They will recline therein on couches and they will find neither excessive heat nor cold.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5605,
            "text": "The shades of the garden will be closely spread over them and it will be easy for them to reach the fruits.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5606,
            "text": "They will be served with silver dishes and crystal clear goblets.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5607,
            "text": "Also there will be crystal clear goblets of silver containing the exact measure of drink which they desire.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5608,
            "text": "They will drink cups containing (soft flowing) sparkling water",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5609,
            "text": "from a spring named salsabil.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5610,
            "text": "They will be served by immortal youths who look like scattered pearls.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5611,
            "text": "If you were to see it, you would find it to be a great kingdom with great bounty.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5612,
            "text": "They will have fine green silk and brocade, and they will be decked with bracelets of silver. Their Lord will provide them with a drink of pure wine.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5613,
            "text": "This will be their reward and their efforts will be appreciated.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5614,
            "text": "(Muhammad), We have revealed the Quran to you in gradual steps.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5615,
            "text": "So wait patiently for the command of your Lord and do not yield to any sinful or disbelieving person among them (people).",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5616,
            "text": "Mention the Name of your Lord, mornings and evenings.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5617,
            "text": "Prostrate before Him and glorify Him extensively during the night.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5618,
            "text": "These people (disbelievers) love the worldly life and neglect the terrifying day which will come.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5619,
            "text": "We have created them and have given them strength. Had We wanted, We could have replaced them with another people like them.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5620,
            "text": "This chapter is a reminder. Let those who want, seek guidance from their Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5621,
            "text": "(The virtuous mentioned in this chapter) want only what God wants. God is All-knowing and All-wise.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5622,
            "text": "He admits to His mercy whomever He wants. For the unjust He has prepared a painful punishment.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 77,
        "name": "سُورَةُ المُرۡسَلَاتِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Mursalaat",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Emissaries",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5623,
            "text": "By (the angels) sent forth with the commands of God,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5624,
            "text": "by (the angels) as swift as blowing winds,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5625,
            "text": "by (the angels) spreading (the words of God) far and wide,",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5626,
            "text": "by (the angels) who make a clear distinction between right and wrong",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5627,
            "text": "and by those who reveal revelations (to the prophets)",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5628,
            "text": "to provide excuses for some and to give warnings to others:",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5629,
            "text": "that whatever with which you have been warned will inevitably come to pass.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5630,
            "text": "Then the stars will lose their light.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5631,
            "text": "Heavens will rent asunder.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5632,
            "text": "The mountains will be blown away as dust.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5633,
            "text": "The Messengers will receive their appointments.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5634,
            "text": "If one asks, 'To which day have such calamitous events been postponed?'",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5635,
            "text": "one will be told,'To the Day of Distinction'.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5636,
            "text": "Would that you knew about the Day of Judgment!",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5637,
            "text": "On that day, woe will be to those who have rejected God's revelations!",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5638,
            "text": "Did We not destroy the ancient people",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5639,
            "text": "and make others settle after them in their land?",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5640,
            "text": "Thus do We deal with the sinful ones.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5641,
            "text": "On that day, woe upon those who have rejected God's revelations!",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5642,
            "text": "Did We not create you from an insignificant drop of fluid",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5643,
            "text": "and place it in a secure place",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5644,
            "text": "for an appointed time?",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5645,
            "text": "Thus did We Plan and how excellent is Our planning!",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5646,
            "text": "On that day, woe would be upon those who have rejected the revelations of God!",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5647,
            "text": "Did We not make the earth as a gathering place",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
