            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5676,
            "text": "(What they think is certainly despicable!). They will soon come to know (the reality).",
