            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5727,
            "text": "(Muhammad), have you heard the story of Moses",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5728,
            "text": "when his Lord called him in the holy valley of Tuwa,",
