            "number": 5876,
            "text": "a spring, the nearest ones to God will drink from it.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5877,
            "text": "The sinners had been laughing at the believers.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5878,
            "text": "When passing by them, they would wink at one another",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5879,
            "text": "and, on returning to their people, boast about what they had done.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5880,
            "text": "On seeing the believers, they would say, 'These people have gone astray'.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5881,
            "text": "No one has appointed them to watch over the believers.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5882,
            "text": "On the Day of Judgment, the believers will laugh at the disbelievers",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5883,
            "text": "while reclining on couches and reviewing (the bounties given to them).",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5884,
            "text": "Will not the disbelievers then be duly recompensed for their laughing at the believers?",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 84,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الانشِقَاقِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Inshiqaaq",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Splitting Open",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5885,
            "text": "When the heavens are rent asunder",
