            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5886,
            "text": "in obedience to the commands of their Lord which are incumbent on them,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5887,
            "text": "when the earth is stretched out",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5888,
            "text": "and throws out of itself all that it contains",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5889,
            "text": "in obedience to the commands of its Lord which are incumbent on it, (the human being will receive due recompense for his deeds).",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5890,
            "text": "Human being, you strive hard to get closer to your Lord, and so you will certainly receive the recompense (of your deeds).",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5891,
            "text": "The reckoning of those whose Book of records will be given into their right hands",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5892,
            "text": "will be easy,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5893,
            "text": "and they will return to their people, delighted",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5894,
            "text": "But as for those whose Book of records will be given behind their backs,",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5895,
            "text": "they will say, 'Woe to us!'",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5896,
            "text": "They will suffer the heat of hell fire.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5897,
            "text": "They lived among their people joyfully",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5898,
            "text": "and had thought that they would never be brought back to life again.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5899,
            "text": "This is a fact. Their Lord is Well-Aware of (all that they do).",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5900,
            "text": "I do not need to swear by the sunset,",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5901,
            "text": "or by the night in which things all come together to rest,",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5902,
            "text": "or by the moon when it is full,",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5903,
            "text": "that you will certainly pass through one stage after another.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5904,
            "text": "What is the matter with them? Why do they not believe?",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5905,
            "text": "Why, when the Quran is recited to them, do they not prostrate themselves?",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": {
              "id": 14,
              "recommended": true,
              "obligatory": false
            }
          },
          {
            "number": 5906,
            "text": "In fact, they reject the Quran,",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5907,
            "text": "but God knows best whatever they accumulate in their hearts.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5908,
            "text": "(Muhammad), tell them that they will all suffer a painful torment",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5909,
            "text": "except the righteously striving believers, who will receive a never-ending reward.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 526,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 85,
        "name": "سُورَةُ البُرُوجِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Burooj",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Constellations",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5910,
            "text": "By the heavens with constellations,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5911,
            "text": "by the promised day,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5912,
            "text": "and by the witness (Muhammad) and that which is witnessed (the Day of Judgment),",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5913,
            "text": "may the people be condemned those who tortured (the believers) in ditches",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5914,
            "text": "by a burning fire",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5915,
            "text": "while they themselves sat around it",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5916,
            "text": "witnessing what they were doing.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5917,
            "text": "The only reason for which they tormented the believers was the latter's belief in God, the Majestic, and Praiseworthy.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5918,
            "text": "and the One to whom belongs the heavens and the earth. God is the Witness of all things.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5919,
            "text": "Those who persecute the believing men and women without repenting will suffer the torment of hell and that of the burning fire.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5920,
            "text": "As for the righteously striving believers, they will live in Paradise wherein streams flow. This is the greatest triumph.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5921,
            "text": "The vengeance of God is terribly severe.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5922,
            "text": "It is He who creates all things and causes them to return.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5923,
            "text": "He is the All-forgiving, the Most Loving One,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5924,
            "text": "the Owner of the Throne, the Glorious One,",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5925,
            "text": "and the Most Effective in His decision.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5926,
            "text": "Have you not heard about the stories of the armies",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5927,
            "text": "of the Pharaoh and Thamud?",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5928,
            "text": "In fact, the disbelievers had always rejected (Our revelations).",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5929,
            "text": "However, God encompassed their activities.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5930,
            "text": "What is revealed to you is certainly a glorious Quran",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5931,
            "text": "that exists in a well-guarded tablet.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 86,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الطَّارِقِ",
        "englishName": "At-Taariq",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Morning Star",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5932,
            "text": "By the heavens and al-tariq.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 528,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5933,
            "text": "Do you know what al-tariq is?",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 528,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5934,
            "text": "(It is a nightly radiant star).",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 528,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5935,
            "text": "There is no soul which is not guarded (by the two angels who record all of its deeds).",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 528,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5936,
            "text": "Let the human being reflect that from what he has been created.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 528,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5937,
            "text": "He has been created from an ejected drop of fluid",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 528,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5938,
            "text": "which comes out of the loins and ribs.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 528,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5939,
            "text": "God has all power to resurrect him.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 528,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5940,
            "text": "On the day when all secrets will be made public,",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 528,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5941,
            "text": "he will have no power, nor anyone to help him.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 528,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5942,
            "text": "By the rotating heavens",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 528,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5943,
            "text": "and the replenishing earth,",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 528,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5944,
            "text": "the Quran is the final word,",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 528,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5945,
            "text": "and it is certainly not a jest.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 528,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5946,
            "text": "They (disbelievers) plot every evil plan,",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 528,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5947,
            "text": "but I too plan against them.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 528,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5948,
            "text": "Give respite to the disbelievers and leave them alone for a while.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 528,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 87,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الأَعۡلَىٰ",
        "englishName": "Al-A'laa",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Most High",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5949,
            "text": "(Muhammad), glorify the Name of your lord, the Most High,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5950,
            "text": "Who has created (all things) proportionately,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5951,
            "text": "decreed their destinies, and provided them with guidance.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5952,
            "text": "It is He who has caused the grass to grow,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5953,
            "text": "then caused it to wither away.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5954,
            "text": "We shall teach you (the Quran) and you will not forget it",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5955,
            "text": "unless God wills it to be otherwise. He knows all that is made public and all that remains hidden.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5956,
            "text": "We shall make all your tasks easy.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5957,
            "text": "Therefore, keep on preaching as long as it is of benefit.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5958,
            "text": "Those who have fear of God will benefit",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5959,
            "text": "but the reprobates will turn away",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5960,
            "text": "and suffer the heat of the great fire",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5961,
            "text": "wherein they will neither live nor die.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5962,
            "text": "Lasting happiness will be for those who purify themselves,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5963,
            "text": "remember the name of the Lord, and pray to Him.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 591,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5964,
            "text": "However, (the disbelievers) prefer the worldly life",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5965,
            "text": "even though the life hereafter will be better and will last forever.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5966,
            "text": "This is what is written in the ancient heavenly Books,",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5967,
            "text": "the Scriptures of Abraham and Moses.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 529,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 88,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الغَاشِيَةِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Ghaashiya",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Overwhelming",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5968,
            "text": "Have you heard the story of the overwhelming event (the Day of Judgment)?",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5969,
            "text": "On that day the faces of some people will be humbly cast down,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5970,
            "text": "troubled and tired as a result of their deeds in the past.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5971,
            "text": "They will suffer the heat of the blazing fire",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5972,
            "text": "and will be made to drink from a fiercely boiling spring.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5973,
            "text": "They will have no food other than bitter and thorny fruit",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5974,
            "text": "which will neither fatten them nor satisfy them.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5975,
            "text": "However, on that day the faces of other people will be happy.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5976,
            "text": "and pleased with the result of their deeds in the past.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5977,
            "text": "They will live in an exalted garden",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5978,
            "text": "wherein they will not hear any vain talk.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5979,
            "text": "Therein will be a flowing spring,",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5980,
            "text": "raised couches,",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5981,
            "text": "well arranged goblets,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5982,
            "text": "well-placed cushions,",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5983,
            "text": "and well spread carpets.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5984,
            "text": "Have they not looked at how the camel is created,",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5985,
            "text": "how the heavens are raised up high,",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5986,
            "text": "how the mountains are set firm,",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5987,
            "text": "and how the earth is spread out?",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5988,
            "text": "(Muhammad), preach; you are only a preacher.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5989,
            "text": "You do not have full control over them.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5990,
            "text": "However, those who turn away and disbelieve,",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5991,
            "text": "God will punish them with the greatest torment.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5992,
            "text": "To Us they will all return.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5993,
            "text": "In Our hands are their accounts.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 592,
            "ruku": 530,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 89,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الفَجۡرِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Fajr",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Dawn",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5994,
            "text": "By the dawn,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5995,
            "text": "by the Ten (secret) Nights,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5996,
            "text": "by the odd and even (8th and 9th Dhil-hajj)",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5997,
            "text": "and by the night when it moves on towards daybreak (reward and retribution in the next life is an absolute reality).",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5998,
            "text": "Is this not a sufficient oath for intelligent people?",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5999,
            "text": "(Muhammad), consider how your Lord dealt with the tribe of Ad,",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6000,
            "text": "the people of the huge columned city of Eram",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6001,
            "text": "whose like has never been created in any other land.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6002,
            "text": "(Also consider how He dealt with) the Thamud, who carved their houses out of the rocks in the valley.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6003,
            "text": "(Also consider the people of) the Pharaoh who victimized people by placing them on the stake,",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6004,
            "text": "led rebellious lives,",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6005,
            "text": "and spread much corruption in the land.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6006,
            "text": "Thus, your Lord afflicted them with torment;",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6007,
            "text": "your Lord keeps an eye on (all evil-doing people).",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6008,
            "text": "As for the human being, when his Lord tests him, honors him, and grants him bounty, he says, 'God has honored me'.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6009,
            "text": "However, when his Lord tests him by a measured amount of sustenance, he says, 'God has disgraced me'.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6010,
            "text": "(Since wealth does not necessarily guarantee everlasting happiness) then why do you not show kindness to the orphans,",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6011,
            "text": "or urge one another to feed the destitute?",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6012,
            "text": "Why do you take away the inheritance of others indiscriminately",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6013,
            "text": "and why do you have an excessive love of riches?",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6014,
            "text": "When the earth is crushed into small pieces",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6015,
            "text": "and (when you find yourself) in the presence of your Lord and the rows and rows of angels, your greed for riches will certainly be of no avail to you.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6016,
            "text": "On that day, hell will be brought closer and the human being will come to his senses, but this will be of no avail to him.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6017,
            "text": "He will say, 'Would that I had done some good deeds for this life'.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6018,
            "text": "On that day the punishment of God and His detention will be unparalleled.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6019,
            "text": "And His bonds will be such as none other can bind.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6020,
            "text": "Serene soul,",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6021,
            "text": "return to your Lord well pleased with him and He will be pleased with you.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6022,
            "text": "Enter among My servants",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6023,
            "text": "into My Paradise.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 90,
        "name": "سُورَةُ البَلَدِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Balad",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The City",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6024,
            "text": "I do not (need to) swear by this town (Mecca)",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6025,
            "text": "in which you are now living",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6026,
            "text": "or by the great father and his wonderful son (Abraham and Ishmael)",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6027,
            "text": "that We have created the human being to face a great deal of hardship.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6028,
            "text": "Does He think that no one will ever have control over him?",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6029,
            "text": "(He boasts and shows off) saying, 'I have spent a great deal of money (for the cause of God)'.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6030,
            "text": "Does he think that no one has seen him?",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6031,
            "text": "Have We not given him two eyes,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6032,
            "text": "a tongue, and two lips?",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6033,
            "text": "Have We not shown him the ways of good and evil?",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6034,
            "text": "Yet, he has not entered into Aqaba",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6035,
            "text": "Would that you knew what Aqaba is!",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6036,
            "text": "It is the setting free of a slave",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6037,
            "text": "or, in a day of famine, the feeding of",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6038,
            "text": "an orphaned relative",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6039,
            "text": "and downtrodden destitute person, (so that he would be of)",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6040,
            "text": "the believers who cooperate with others in patience (steadfastness) and kindness.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6041,
            "text": "These are the people of the right hand.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6042,
            "text": "As for those who disbelieve in Our revelations, they are the people of the left",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6043,
            "text": "who will be engulfed in the fire.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 91,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الشَّمۡسِ",
        "englishName": "Ash-Shams",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Sun",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6044,
            "text": "By the sun and its noon-time brightness,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6045,
            "text": "by the moon when it follows the sun,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6046,
            "text": "by the day when it brightens the earth,",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6047,
            "text": "by the night when it covers the earth with darkness,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6048,
            "text": "by the heavens and that (Power) which established them,",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6049,
            "text": "by the earth and that (Power) which spread it out",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6050,
            "text": "and by the soul and that (Power) which designed it",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6051,
            "text": "and inspired it with knowledge of evil and piety,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6052,
            "text": "those who purify their souls will certainly have everlasting happiness",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6053,
            "text": "and those who corrupt their souls will certainly be deprived (of happiness).",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6054,
            "text": "The people of Thamud rejected (the truth) as a result of their rebelliousness",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6055,
            "text": "when the most corrupt of them incited them (to commit evil).",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6056,
            "text": "The Messenger of God told them, 'This is a she-camel, belonging to God. Do not deprive her of her share of water'.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6057,
            "text": "However, they rejected him and slew her. So their Lord completely destroyed them and their city for their sins.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6058,
            "text": "God is not afraid of the result of what He had decreed.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 533,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 92,
        "name": "سُورَةُ اللَّيۡلِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Lail",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Night",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
