            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6060,
            "text": "by the day when it appears radiant,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 595,
            "ruku": 534,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6061,
            "text": "and by that (Power) which created the male and female,",
